titles.title: A resolution to authorize the printing of additional copies of a Senate report entitled "Developments in Aging: 1992".

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.

bill.summary: 3/31/1993--Introduced. Authorizes the printing of additional copies of the annual report of the Special Committee on Aging to the Senate, entitled "Developments in Aging: 1992."
